{"tid":2490063,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★馬雲現身俄羅斯地理學會會議！只是聆聽 未見發言 ，偶爾喝茶","createTime":"2021-04-15T10:25:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T10:42:23.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ea6cf2370fccef3f78e3b04c7ec508f2f10eb050","tid":2490063,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T10:25:47.000Z","msg":"外媒報道，已鮮有露面的馬雲，近日竟現身出席俄羅斯總統普京召開的俄羅斯地理學會監事會會議。<br />\n<br />\n據俄羅斯傳媒報道，馬雲是通過網絡視訊會議系統出席會議，當時他身後房間內布局是採用中國風，牆上有畫着梅花。全程近2小時的會議，馬雲並沒有發言，<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>一直只是聆聽其他與會者交流和報告，偶爾喝茶。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20210415/bkn-20210415105532860-0415_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20210415%2Fbkn-20210415105532860-0415_00842_001.html&d=Uh5SjXth0XRRLWSKrhPNwMorGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=4cbd7493\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20210415/bkn-20210415105532860-0415_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"5cbd44fa1a4a1c0792d0e7ddcfa584e5879a8df6","tid":2490063,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T10:25:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cff3a91366ea7b866260d6ea998b284d343418f0","tid":2490063,"uid":237562,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T10:27:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYBtvRQsj1w9ohLmVpaMJMAqW9g2BC8BntTKA4kBsbmAn?filename=jCph3wX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjCph3wX.jpg&h=548b95d2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c407206aba94c14acb6724a014e4ce4ae8f3beda","tid":2490063,"uid":321977,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score"